9 June 2008Minister Essop Pahad will have a post Budget Vote briefing on behalf of The Presidency, to elaborate on issues raised during the debate, clarify matters raised and interact in general with the media.The briefing will take place as follows:Date: Thursday, 12 June 2008 Time: 15h00 - 16h00 Venue: Imbizo Media Centre 120 Plein Street, Cape TownEnquiries Colin Cruywagen Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)